room_title: Escape room "The Gambler" by Breakout KC in Kansas City
review: Always an awesome time! The lady at the counter is always energetic and smiling. Our favorite big brother voice is definitely Cody lol. Keep up the great work.

room_title: Escape room "The Gambler" by Breakout KC in Kansas City
review: Went for my birthday last night and it was so much fun!! Everyone had a really great time!! Definitely going to try every room, 1 down 3 to go!!

room_title: Escape room "The Gambler" by Breakout KC in Kansas City
review: This was such a fun experience!!!! We escaped The River Quay Casino Room with only 5 Seconds to spare!

room_title: Escape room "The Gambler" by Breakout KC in Kansas City
review: Went with my co-workers from Jaegerz Laser Tag. We were so close but really had a great time!! Will be back to try the other rooms!!! Thank you guys!!!!

room_title: Escape room "The Gambler" by Breakout KC in Kansas City
review: This was amazing! We were in the casino room and it was a blast! Highly recommend !

room_title: Escape room "The Gambler" by Breakout KC in Kansas City
review: I loved breakout KC! It is definitely a challenge and we were so close to breaking out on time! The staff were friendly and helpful as well! If you're wanting to do something fun and different this is it! My friends and I definitely plan on returning.

room_title: Escape room "The Gambler" by Breakout KC in Kansas City
review: We went for friends birthday last night. The room was definitely challenging (we did the casino room) but it was a lot of fun! The staff was great and we definitely got our money's worth! Can't wait to go again!
